title: Handshake Medium Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone

adjectives: Represents a pact made with a warm embrace.
verbs: To come together and seal a deal with a firm grasp.
nouns: A symbol of unity and mutual understanding.

description: Represents a handshake between two people with medium skin tone and medium-dark skin tone, signifying agreement, partnership, or a friendly greeting.
apple_vendor_description: This handshake emoji on Apple devices depicts two hands meeting with a warm, inviting gesture, rendered in medium-light and medium-dark skin tones respectively. Apple's characteristic smooth gradients and realistic lighting create a sense of genuine connection and agreement between the two palms. The soft, rounded edges of the hands contribute to a friendly and approachable feel, making it a perfect symbol of partnership, trust, or a successful deal.
